messages.content: ComfyUI-Geowizard is a wrapper node that allows the use of Geowizard in ComfyUI.
How are models downloaded in ComfyUI-Geowizard?
Models are automatically downloaded from the original source to 'ComfyUI/models/diffusers/geowizard' in ComfyUI-Geowizard.
What is the approximate size of the downloaded models in ComfyUI-Geowizard?
The approximate size of the downloaded models in ComfyUI-Geowizard is around 4.7GB.
What is the original repository for Geowizard?
The original repository for Geowizard is https://github.com/fuxiao0719/GeoWizard.
Is there a Hugging Face space associated with Geowizard?
Yes, there is a Hugging Face space associated with Geowizard, which is https://huggingface.co/spaces/lemonaddie/geowizard/.
